{"tid":2137020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"試過上網賣嘢嘅入嚟 真人真事","createTime":"2020-08-02T14:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T14:48:10.000Z","uid":236993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9280485ec55bb909ccebb8ec3434fc1fda4200fd","tid":2137020,"uid":236993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T14:38:29.000Z","msg":"自己本身呢排試下網上賣野，賣game AC<br />\n<br />\n第一次就收alipayHK<br />\n第二次就 賣家要求我畀 銀行戶口同名<br />\n開頭我覺得正常照畀, 又加wts之後問野<br />\n<br />\n跟住就開始慢慢用隻game嘅安全性問題問我個人資料, 隻game要 生日日期， <br />\n<br />\n呢個時候佢已經基本上有我<br />\n1電話<br />\n2銀行戶口<br />\n3本人全名<br />\n<br />\n 跟住 我 叫佢cap圖畀我 確認一下 保障大家,而 佢亦都好多解釋, 支吾以對 ，就係死都唔cap圖畀我 ， 仲話個問題, (要我生日日期) 係突然之間 螢幕 彈出嚟cap唔切<br />\n<br />\n之後我問番佢 入到未 佢又話突然入到 AC,<br />\n<br />\n然後我係咁關心佢, 佢都亦冇再覆我啦<br />\n<br />\n第一次賣Game account <br />\nSor1999"},{"pid":"253f1fd002c717afaea7c6c8819b093c734d9ca6","tid":2137020,"uid":236993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T14:39:26.000Z","msg":"樓主太多疑慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb96109eb36cda2151cc85aee09836f0083cc2d1","tid":2137020,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T14:40:17.000Z","msg":"Alipay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3f058dfb7eebe4cbbcee83bbdb8a0dc51ad9ea","tid":2137020,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T14:42:04.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">西九龍影相手足被控襲警 聽朝9:30西九龍裁判法院提堂</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2136461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2136461</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6fSFYYC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6fSFYYC.jpg&h=e1467aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FusbmbR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFusbmbR.jpg&h=51fd69ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6deb551011f21a10256dc373